OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter police stabbed in Worcestershire
OL,6,FA man has been charged with attempted
OL,7,Fmurder after a police officer was
OL,8,Fstabbed in Worcestershire.
OL,10,F25-year-old Soul Henry of no fixed
OL,11,Fabode was also charged with burglary,
OL,12,Fpossession of a bladed article and
OL,13,Fanimal cruelty.
OL,15,FIt follows an incident in Clifton,
OL,16,Fnear Kempsey, on Sunday.
OL,18,FHenry will appear at Kidderminster
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday, 22nd
OL,20,FApril.
